
1.Install Velodyne binary packages on ROS Kinetic:
sudo apt-get install ros-kinetic-hector-gazebo-plugins

or from source code:
cd ~/catkin_ws/src/ROS
git clone https://github.com/tu-darmstadt-ros-pkg/hector_gazebo.git
git clone https://github.com/tu-darmstadt-ros-pkg/hector_models.git 
cd ~/catkin_ws
catkin_make
source ./devel/setup.bash

2. Start the Simulation:
download directory "sensor_sim_gazebo"
roslaunch sensor_sim_gazebo laser.launch


